{"tid":548881,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"以為母親投井自盡　沙頭角孝子跳入井中救母","createTime":"2018-02-03T05:32:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-11T08:07:39.000Z","uid":20933,"like":237,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":60,"replies":[{"pid":"cdcc6cb7e959058bfb3f0e2df52e9bee148bf540","tid":548881,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T05:32:00.000Z","msg":"沙頭角坪軬路隔田村，中午12時許，一名男子目睹母親投入井內，一度懷疑對方尋死，奮不顧身跳落井中救母。消防接報到場，救起兩人，老婦否認自殺，聲稱失去平衡墮井。<br />\n<br />\n老婦懷疑在事件中受寒，蓋上保暖氈送院，兒子則無恙，毋須送院，案件列作「有人意外受傷」處理。"},{"pid":"06572b79ac223fefb7cf92ad13abb938e055327c","tid":548881,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T05:32:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180203/s00001/1517634459809\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180203%2Fs00001%2F1517634459809&d=zRDvmxCS8mYNeMIDAQYKsf1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=ec7e3ad2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180203%2Fs00001%2F1517634459809&h=869d21d3\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180203/s00001/1517634459809</a>"},{"pid":"86b5845c4d92e04529a277fcdb37e9c7e4a05b41","tid":548881,"uid":3189,"like":188,"dislike":0,"score":188,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T05:48:19.000Z","msg":"古法自殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed61f8fa4fda415bb57ef325028002aca18cc247","tid":548881,"uid":57705,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T05:49:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f1f84bd96a60ecc7c7fda17d5b7338b88f20c03a","tid":548881,"uid":87560,"like":88,"dislike":0,"score":88,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T05:52:44.000Z","msg":"咁凍跳井<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bfd3dae7d3218fe234c0aa480ed00aa775722ce","tid":548881,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,