除"},{"pid":"8ace3ce13173991fbd6d780f2db652737d1e882a","tid":548881,"uid":37220,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T06:16:34.000Z","msg":"孝子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5dd3eaad6e691594310800d049054e348834b0f","tid":548881,"uid":67500,"like":12,"dislike":2,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T06:21:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/pPAWrb0t8YQ?t=6m49s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FpPAWrb0t8YQ%3Ft%3D6m49s&d=zRDvmxCS8mYNeMIDAQYKsf1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=79555d37\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/pPAWrb0t8YQ?t=6m49s</a>"},{"pid":"004abaa2fa115eef2deced2c3dd47491abc9a5d2","tid":548881,"uid":106211,"like":6,"dislike":13,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T14:36:47.000Z","msg":"老母本身死唔去 男子跳落去反而壓死佢老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb5009fb875dba5e34082bea5618e6d616988337","tid":548881,"uid":45368,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T14:39:27.000Z","msg":"唔睇真d以為係強國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7ae9077a934914f7bcf94549cc40f332d9363e6","tid":548881,"uid":20933,"like":44,"dislike":0,"score":44,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T17:07:07.000Z","msg":"現場消息稱，婆婆檢查水泵期間，帽子不慎跌入井內，她爬落井企圖執帽，其間跣腳墮井底。<br />\n<br />\n打鼓嶺坪輋隔田村一個水井，早上11時許，77歲姓廖老婦意外跌落井內，其張姓兒子獲悉立即跳下救母，雙雙困在井內，消防接報到場將兩母子救出，兩人均清醒，兒子無受傷，母親則送院治理，警方正調查事件，將案件列作有人意外受傷處理。<br />\n<br />\n據坪輋附近一個農場的場主傅太表示，水井是多年前村民種菜用的，惟近年菜農已撤走，現在是公用的，水井用作淋花或洗滌用途，有30多呎深，肇事婆婆有水喉駁至水井，據說早兩日水泵有問題，婆婆的兒子曾拉出抽水泵洗泥，惟今日可能又有問題，婆婆由井底拉起水泵檢查。現場消息稱，婆婆檢查水泵期間，帽子不慎跌入井內，她爬落井企圖執帽，其間跣腳墮井底。<br />\n<br />\n婆婆的張姓女兒事後亦在醫院表示，母親是執帽而意外跌入井。<br />\n<br />\n有份救人的傅太指，平日井口用鐵絲網蓋住，又有石頭壓着鐵絲網，「如果唔刻意打開個網，唔會有任何嘢跌落去。」她指婆婆以「壁虎功」兩手撐著井壁爬落井，其間疑跣腳困在10多呎深的水井內，半身浸濕，當時她與媳婦一起，但其媳婦既無報警，又不懂叫救命，只懂找其丈夫（即婆婆的兒子）前來查看，兒子目睹母親困在井內，立即爬落井救母不果，雙雙困在10多呎深的井內，此時傅太與其員工聽到大陣嘈雜聲，以為有人「打仔」，遂出來查看，始知兩母子同被困井內，取來20呎長梯欲救卻不夠長掉在井底，只好放繩讓兒子捉實，「佢擘開腳撐住個井，又要攬住阿媽」，情況狼狽不堪。稍後消防到場先後救出兩人，婆婆須送院治理。"},{"pid":"0a8b63d69af1cddf648da538cc9bab6c9740fc7f","tid":548881,"uid":70448,"like":98,"dislike":1,"score":97,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T17:16:00.000Z","msg":"連埋條梯同繩<br />\n不停掉野落個井<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23c89ebaf1eebc5ef9f0e18d75d9faa304f973b6","tid":548881,"uid":85163,"like":1,"dislike":37,"score":-36,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T17:19:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f077b385b51de106f222c76374c6d73a25d239c6","tid":548881,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T17:29:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b86888d4002aabe7f36fe23f5c9ec33c769a1f9","tid":548881,"uid":69013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T17:37:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94cf630bac09930f2d3502529bb4f3c565762e63","tid":548881,"uid":104443,"like":47,"dislike":2,"score":45,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T17:38:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">以上五毛：<br />\n<br />\ndewi👿<br />\nEpiphany</span></span>"},{"pid":"a173e151bf3d162be282aa448c95892175d63f21","tid":548881,"uid":14918,"like":97,"dislike":0,"score":97,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T17:39:20.000Z","msg":"77歲玩壁虎功落井<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b233027aa865a085c01cafc647a4c9d30c81829b","tid":548881,"uid":550,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T18:26:20.000Z","msg":"原來沙頭角仲要打井取水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n原來仲有人會投井自盡<img src=\"/assets/faces/norma